metatags.og:description: What is Georgia ID on iPhone and Apple Watch?Georgia ID on iPhone and Apple Watch is a voluntary, secure, digitized version of your Georgia-issued driver's license (DL) or identification card (ID) available in the Apple Wallet app on your iPhone and Apple Watch.
metatags.twitter:description: What is Georgia ID on iPhone and Apple Watch?Georgia ID on iPhone and Apple Watch is a voluntary, secure, digitized version of your Georgia-issued driver's license (DL) or identification card (ID) available in the Apple Wallet app on your iPhone and Apple Watch.
